Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做克劳德˙肯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能够揭发『魔石索沙』所隐藏的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便和蕾娜开始朝着艾尔大陆前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少用你们那双脏手随便碰我!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来在途中遇到了纹章术师塞丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又和一个叫做艾修顿的剑客变成了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我体内沉睡红莲之火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉火王派蒙之名解放你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请依圣三角的引导
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将站在我眼前的愚昧者，给予灼热的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳为什么要离开阿利亚村
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还跟那两个家伙一起旅行呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在找魔石索沙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和克劳德为了调查魔石索沙的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必须到艾尔大陆去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我听说魔石索沙带来的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本超乎我们的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎么还会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当这块大地－艾克斯贝尔受到欺凌民不聊生之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便会出现一位异国打扮的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者高举着光剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救苦难的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德就是传说中的这位勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好朋友…啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为了帮他们寻宝和驱魔，虽然多绕了一点远路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过折腾了半天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算到达了克洛斯大陆东部的港湾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是哈利啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里热热闹闹的，挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海风吹起来也好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要把谜底解开…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事啊我们待会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先找间旅馆好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了每天餐风露宿的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要拉我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子好饿、背酸得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发干燥，皮肤也快干死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说也对耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会给人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个没用的剑客到底跑到哪里去了嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(来看一看啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(新到的货色哪)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我这里的货色最齐全哪)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请问你，到底要摸到什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你们的朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把他弄走好不好啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这是克洛斯l3世纪的橡木桶欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种遥远又古老的香味…\N你一定装过白兰地对不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真香，闻到我都快要醉倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他刚刚到现在就是这样没离开过耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他该不会是个…迷恋酒桶的收集狂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么收集狂啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上有这种人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卖你们5000弗尔就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很贵吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要买啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还真的要背着这个大酒桶去艾尔大陆啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要傻了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是艾修顿他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠们都在向你求救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样…就买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个酒桶该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25午前在卡利亚工房限量生产的…桧木酒桶吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便他了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小长和小圆不会有什么事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经把塞丽奴的帽子挂在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他应该很快就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像他那种人啊…为他担心根本是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:07:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样倒也罢了，要是迷路的话怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，妳就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯国王给我们的通行证\N能不能借给我看看呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…哪里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象…看不到海了耶?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们…是迷路啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有，没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想休息的时候，我们去看要搭的船吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是，我们马上就要过海了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是得整顿一下心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟…有没有搞错啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腿肿得这么厉害好惨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳又来了，那妳先等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去拿一些热水来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感激妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~喂~喂~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，眼睛突然有一点刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是灰尘跑进去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是睫毛长反了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳最好不要揉得太用力，我来帮妳看一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴姐也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，她的纹章术会帮上克劳德不少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不要计较这些事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴姐，热水…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜、蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~太好了…碰上好人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也听到蕾娜说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才，从她站的位置看起来，也难怪她会误会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差那么多…不会吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们…竟然接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩个搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道一定是妳，蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪，我们能在这里碰面还真是巧耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…我们离山越来越近了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是方向…好象错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么啊你?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把房间钥匙通通都交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们兄弟要到你这里来找样宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请妳下次再来捧场哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…蕾娜，妳会不会吃得太多啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土产吃太多肚子会胀耶?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓，我要全部吃光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃东西的时候不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，喝点水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳还好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德也太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这件事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自己说这趟旅行可能要豁出性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还做出那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要继续不停的吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀蕾娜 好了啦!妳冷静一点  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳放手，放手放手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么『整顿一下心情』嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我才不要跟着他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就让我继续吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦，不要闹了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是克劳德他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不像是这样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲眼看到的不可能错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…妳要回阿利亚村喽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳不想跟他一起旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这里也不是办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那里吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点，先溜为妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德在里面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛，明明是你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…那是我的包包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕，快溜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，把我的包包还我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，妳追去太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是通行证在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强盗、有强盗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是小雪吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎么会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些待会再说!蕾娜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想念妳啊…妳好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你的样子好象不怎么好哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了一件大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把包包还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人还不死心啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可见这里面的东西很重要欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它还给我、还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不还
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海水怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，通行证…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，妳没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，快抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，妳快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空…破…斩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德、克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行证…被人偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不能怪妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事都要怪我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用跟我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为塞丽奴姐人那么好，长得又好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我误会了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是妳…误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么…在意克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们刚才还真是千钧一发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快把它解决掉吧，克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，妳让开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀?我怎么会在这个地方啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都在?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来啦?看来你们又合好了嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是通行证…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们三个人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象还蛮满意我天雷电波的威力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，塞丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行证又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我一边卖果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边寻找有哪家店愿意请我去唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌手…好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢唱歌\N人活着总要诚实的面对自己嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，蕾娜也是一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么?船长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不肯开船呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没有听到那个传闻吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一片大海已经不是我们认识的大海了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到魔石的影响，它平就变得不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到连大海也…改变了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是魔石索沙的影响吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔石索沙…

